description: List all of the dedicated IP pools that exist in your Amazon Web Services account in the current Region.

nested_items.name: DedicatedIpPools
nested_items.description: A list of all of the dedicated IP pools that are associated with your Amazon Web Services account in the current Region.

nested_items.name: NextToken
nested_items.description: A token that indicates that there are additional IP pools to list. To view additional IP pools, issue another request to ListDedicatedIpPools, passing this token in the NextToken parameter.
